originalSql:
WITH UserBadgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        COUNT(b.Id) AS BadgeCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GoldCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SilverCount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN b.Class = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BronzeCount
    FROM Users u
    LEFT JOIN Badges b ON u.Id = b.UserId
    GROUP BY u.Id, u.DisplayName
),
PostStats AS (
    SELECT 
        p.OwnerUserId,
        COUNT(p.Id) AS TotalPosts,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 END) AS QuestionCount,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 END) AS AnswerCount,
        SUM(p.Score) AS TotalScore
    FROM Posts p
    GROUP BY p.OwnerUserId
),
CombinedStats AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.DisplayName,
        u.Reputation,
        COALESCE(ub.BadgeCount, 0) AS BadgeCount,
        COALESCE(ub.GoldCount, 0) AS GoldCount,
        COALESCE(ub.SilverCount, 0) AS SilverCount,
        COALESCE(ub.BronzeCount, 0) AS BronzeCount,
        COALESCE(ps.TotalPosts, 0) AS TotalPosts,
        COALESCE(ps.QuestionCount, 0) AS QuestionCount,
        COALESCE(ps.AnswerCount, 0) AS AnswerCount,
        COALESCE(ps.TotalScore, 0) AS TotalScore
    FROM Users u
    LEFT JOIN UserBadgeCounts ub ON u.Id = ub.UserId
    LEFT JOIN PostStats ps ON u.Id = ps.OwnerUserId
)
SELECT 
    UserId,
    DisplayName,
    Reputation,
    BadgeCount,
    GoldCount,
    SilverCount,
    BronzeCount,
    TotalPosts,
    QuestionCount,
    AnswerCount,
    TotalScore
FROM CombinedStats
WHERE TotalPosts > 0
ORDER BY TotalScore DESC, Reputation DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("OwnerUserId", "OwnerUserId") AS "OWNERUSERID", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END AS "FD_COL_1", CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END AS "FD_COL_2", "Score"
FROM "Posts"

SELECT COALESCE("t7"."USERID", "t7"."USERID") AS "USERID", "t7"."DISPLAYNAME", "t7"."REPUTATION", "t7"."BADGECOUNT", "t7"."GOLDCOUNT", "t7"."SILVERCOUNT", "t7"."BRONZECOUNT", "t7"."TOTALPOSTS", "t7"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t7"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t7"."TOTALSCORE"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", CASE WHEN "t3"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."GOLDCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."GOLDCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."SILVERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."SILVERCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."BRONZECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BRONZECOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALPOSTS", CASE WHEN "t4"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZECOUNT"
FROM "Badges"
RIGHT JOIN "Users" AS "Users0" ON "Badges"."UserId" = "Users0"."Id"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", COUNT("FD_COL_1") AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", COUNT("FD_COL_2") AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "OWNERUSERID") AS "t4" ON "Users"."Id" = "t4"."OWNERUSERID"
WHERE CASE WHEN "t4"."TOTALPOSTS" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."TOTALPOSTS" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END > 0
ORDER BY 11 DESC NULLS FIRST, "Users"."Reputation" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t7"
